*imapsync-1.255 (28 Jun 2008)

  28 Jun 2008; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  -imapsync-1.217.ebuild, +imapsync-1.255.ebuild:
  Version bump, #218810

  09 Jun 2008; Torsten Veller <tove@gentoo.org> imapsync-1.217.ebuild:
  Add Digest-HMAC to RDEPEND (#225089). Don't run imapsync during installation
  to minimize DEPEND.

  30 Aug 2007; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing langthang from metadata due to his retirement (see #53239 for
  reference).

*imapsync-1.217 (01 Apr 2007)

  01 Apr 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org>
  -files/imapsync-1.171-gentoo.patch, -files/imapsync-gentoo.patch,
  -files/imapsync-ssl.patch, -imapsync-1.121.ebuild, imapsync-1.182.ebuild,
  +imapsync-1.217.ebuild:
  1.182 stable on x86. Version bump to 1.217. Removed 1.121, as well as
  obsolete patches from FILESDIR.

  25 Mar 2007; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  imapsync-1.182.ebuild:
  ppc stable

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  06 Jan 2007; Fernando J. Pereda <ferdy@gentoo.org> -imapsync-1.171.ebuild,
  -imapsync-1.171-r1.ebuild:
  QA: Clean unused versions.

  10 Dec 2006; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> imapsync-1.171.ebuild,
  imapsync-1.171-r1.ebuild, imapsync-1.182.ebuild:
  Change perl-core/Digest-MD5 and perl-core/MIME-Base64 dependencies to
  appropriate virtuals. Bug #157668 by Jakub Moc <jakub at gentoo.org>.

  18 Sep 2006; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  imapsync-1.182.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc

*imapsync-1.182 (30 Aug 2006)

